    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/learnDita.dita" xtrc="p:1;14:8">From time to time we get requests from beginners or from users migrating from other tools who
      want to start using Oxygen with DITA and they need to know a set of useful resources.</p>
    <section id="section_wyk_5fj_2v" class="- topic/section " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/learnDita.dita" xtrc="section:1;16:38">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/learnDita.dita" xtrc="title:2;17:14">Resources for editing DITA with Oxygen:</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/learnDita.dita" xtrc="p:2;18:10">We have a getting started section in our user's manual: <xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/#topics/eppo-first-dita-topic.html" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/learnDita.dita" xtrc="xref:1;20:43"/> and a larger section on DITA authoring: <xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/#topics/author-dita.html" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/learnDita.dita" xtrc="xref:2;22:43"/>.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/learnDita.dita" xtrc="p:3;23:10">We have a list of videos, some of them DITA-related here: <xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/videos.html" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/learnDita.dita" xtrc="xref:3;24:88"/> and a series
        of past webinar recordings about editing DITA with Oxygen.<dl id="dl_av4_tgf_wpb" class="- topic/dl " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/learnDita.dita" xtrc="dl:1;25:91">
