          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/learnDita.dita" xtrc="li:4;109:15">Mekon: <xref href="http://mekon.com/news/dita-authoring-oxygen-author/" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/learnDita.dita" xtrc="xref:23;110:33"/></li>
          <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/learnDita.dita" xtrc="li:5;111:15">French course by Tireme: <xref href="http://dita.tireme.fr/#definition/m2_session_adapter_dita.html" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/learnDita.dita" xtrc="xref:24;113:33"/></li>
